data.description: Don't miss out on this beautiful 3 bedroom / 2 bath ranch home that sits on a perfect corner lot, in the highly sought after community of Phoenix Crossing. Open concept floorplan boasting plenty of natural lighting that flows into the oversized kitchen with granite countertops, ample cabinet space, and gorgeous wraparound island. Spacious Owner's suite has a large closet, master bath features a walk-in tile shower and dual vanities. Well-sized secondary bedrooms and newly installed fence in the back yard. Located less than 10 miles from Lake Oconee and Lake Sinclair. This home won't last long! 100% USDA ELIGIBLE!
